HEADWORD: Guardroom
<hw>Guard"room`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mil.)</fld>
<def>The room occupied by the guard during its term of duty; also, a
room where prisoners are confined.</def>⟦br⟧
